{"tid":132761,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩方法可以氹到男朋友執房","createTime":"2017-02-24T05:25:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T11:54:38.000Z","uid":85964,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca74e6fb32991cd77c53e3c8c5df5b9b5386e9a","tid":132761,"uid":85964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:25:26.000Z","msg":"男朋友同佢housemate share一間屋<br />\n依加我搬埋入去<br />\n但佢訓單人房<br />\n間房本身已經唔大 <br />\n佢啲野都成日亂擺<br />\n好似嗔完鼻涕啲紙巾成日都掉唔入垃圾桶 <br />\n成地都係紙巾<br />\n然後著完啲衫又掉係地下<br />\n晾完嘅衫 除非我幫佢收衫摺好放埋入櫃桶 <br />\n如果唔係就咁掉入個籃入面 要著先巢<br />\n試過摺完放係床佢都係掉係個籃到<br />\n電腦枱就唔洗講<br />\n啱啱一齊個陣幫佢執 佢仲勁嬲咁話攪到佢啲野唔知放晒係邊<br />\n不過呢次我都明 我無交代清楚 所以之後都唔敢執得太勁 <br />\n 我自己本身已經唔算整齊<br />\n但日日見到間房咁 好崩潰<br />\n我又唔係無執 但次次隔一日就打回原型.....<br />\n同埋佢成日話放工好攰唔想執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人教下我可以點做<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54c9fead9bde7d8cabfcf5f1408c7449bb15d33","tid":132761,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:25:53.000Z","msg":"執完幫佢口爆"},{"pid":"2ce54e9e7b69378a98931400a8bbd80edb255b2f","tid":132761,"uid":85964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:27:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>執完幫佢口爆</blockquote><br />\n我平時已經有 <br />\n係咪唔好咁寵佢好啲...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7905b60ecd8d61f0712231f0e354ce59cc29da7d","tid":132761,"uid":24913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:27:16.000Z","msg":"除左條底褲比佢執濟先"},{"pid":"66b72f673ab752e7c12728d70c0c2658f9a34f18","tid":132761,"uid":85964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:31:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左條底褲比佢執濟先</blockquote><br />\n咁樣佢會反口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffeaf92da6f41b3e7dc687c1d2351e160cfd0ee","tid":132761,"uid":25552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:33:18.000Z","msg